<plot>A documentary giving film fans a behind-the-scenes look at the making this dramatic comedy about three daughters who must deal with their father's declining health. Includes interviews with Meg Ryan, Lisa Kudrow and other members of the cast and crew, who relate some of their experiences with making the film, as well as giving their views on all the work that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573910</url></doc>
